This is an simple example of ANL application. This makes simple histograms and
save them into a ROOT file. 

How to Install:
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ../source -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path/to/install
make
make install

By default, the install destination is your home directory.

How to Run:
cd run
./run_test_histogram.rb

If the run is successful, you will get a ROOT file containing histograms.
Please check it.
